Class HeuristicTree

java.lang.Object
  net.parallaxed.bluejam.NoteTree
      net.parallaxed.bluejam.HeuristicTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Function, Heuristic, NoteSequence
Deprecated. 

public class HeuristicTree
extends NoteTree
implements Heuristic

This class is the cornerstone of the evolution. It provides the base class for all style heuristics. Implementations of HeuristicTree effectively provide the "teaching" basics for the program, guiding the solo in a certain direction. Evolution cycles may occur with or without heuristic trees.

Author:
Ciarán Rowe (csr2@kent.ac.uk)
